Dockside Apartment Homes is located in the premier Lakes neighborhood in Kent, Washington.
We offer richly appointed one, two and three bedroom apartment homes.
Our unique newly renovated homes feature a luxurious white modern kitchen with warm gray cabinets, stainless steel appliances, vinyl flooring a washer and dryer in every home.
Residents enjoy basketball and racquetball in our indoor court, two resort style pools and a business center.
Waterford at the Lakes is minutes from thriving employers such as Showare Center, Kent Station, REI Corporate headquarters and Boeing, as well as I-5 and Hwy-167.
Our pet friendly community offers a picturesque setting, featuring classically styled buildings surrounded by mature tree-lined streets, tranquil lakes and unsurpassed amenities.
Visit us today for a personal tour!
